      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's just a script, isn't it? like what you're supposed to say. but the reality is i've been here a year and i don't have a single person i can actually call. if i just... stopped, the only thing that would change is a landlord finding an empty apartment weeks later. i don't have any weight here. i'm just taking up space.",
